OL,3,CIn Lebanon, choosing where you live
OL,4,Cmay mean choosing where you die
OL,6,FFrom a distance, Lebanon's southern
OL,7,Fsuburbs look like a mass of rubble,
OL,8,Fdamaged and destroyed buildings. Day
OL,9,Fand night, we see and hear the
OL,10,Fexplosions as another missile hits
OL,11,Fthis heavily built-up area.
OL,13,FIt is one of Hezbollah's strongholds,
OL,14,Fand benign smiling images of the late
OL,15,Fformer leader Hassan Nasrallah adorn
OL,16,Fwhat walls are left and the miles of
OL,17,Frubble.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
