OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774480286
OL,3,CIn Lebanon, choosing where you live
OL,4,Cmay mean choosing where you die
OL,6,FThis is where he lived and where he
OL,7,Fdied, and where Israel continues to
OL,8,Fseek out those associated with
OL,9,FHezbollah.
OL,11,FBut it is also a place that is home to
OL,12,Fhundreds of thousands of people.
OL,14,FMany fled on the day the war started
OL,15,Fbut others decided to stay. On our
OL,16,Fbrief journey, we saw some of those
OL,17,Fwho are trying to survive in this
OL,18,Fbattleground.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
