OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774480286
OL,3,CIn Lebanon, choosing where you live
OL,4,Cmay mean choosing where you die
OL,6,FThere were not huge numbers, but still
OL,7,Fsignificantly more than the last war
OL,8,Fin 2024. Some can't afford to be
OL,9,Fdisplaced again, others can't face the
OL,10,Fhumiliation of it.
OL,12,FThey would rather die in their homes
OL,13,Fthan live displaced in their own land.
OL,14,FOne of those who is living there told
OL,15,Fus he waits for the Israeli warnings,
OL,16,Fthen leaves home for a coffee shop a
OL,17,Fshort distance away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
