CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774480286
OL,3,CIn Lebanon, choosing where you live
OL,4,Cmay mean choosing where you die
OL,6,FOnce the bombing subsides he goes
OL,7,Fhome, hoping it's still there. For now
OL,8,Fit is, and in the street by his house
OL,9,Fchildren still play.
OL,11,FIt is a sorry way to live. Lebanon
OL,12,Fonly has a population of six million,
OL,13,Fas a result of this war a million of
OL,14,Fthose are now displaced.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
