CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774480286
OL,3,CIn Lebanon, choosing where you live
OL,4,Cmay mean choosing where you die
OL,6,FOne in six people who cannot safely
OL,7,Flive in their own homes. Some are
OL,8,Flucky enough to have places to go with
OL,9,Ffamily or friends. Others are in
OL,10,Fschools which have become displacement
OL,11,Fshelters, another group living under
OL,12,Ftarpaulin on the streets.
OL,14,FThey are from the southern suburbs and
OL,15,Ffrom the south of the country, where
OL,16,FIsraeli troops now occupy land from
OL,17,Fthe border north.
OL,19,FMost of the villages there are also
OL,20,Fempty, but in some there remain those
OL,21,Fwho refuse to leave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
